metadata.name: RTS: Neo Tokyo
metadata.description: The 'RTS: Neo Tokyo' NFT is the first non randomized banner from RTS that was sold exclusivly to holders of the Neo Tokyo Citizen and Neo Tokyo Outer Citizen collection. Buying this NFT will enable you to use the 3, 5 and 6 frame version of this room on the dapp, even if you do not hold an Neo Tokyo NFT.
